163
00:11:22,682 --> 00:11:24,809
Aku juga mau!

164
00:11:24,934 --> 00:11:27,561
Kau takkan bisa makan malam
jika makan itu!

165
00:11:27,645 --> 00:11:29,313
Aku yang menyalakan api!

166
00:11:29,397 --> 00:11:31,649
- Berikan bagianku!
- Ya!

167
00:11:31,732 --> 00:11:32,817
Berikan bagianku!

168
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:34,276
Hei!

169
00:11:36,987 --> 00:11:40,741
Kami baru dapat kabar
naga muncul di kota sebelah!

170
00:11:40,908 --> 00:11:42,535
Ada lagi?

171
00:11:42,785 --> 00:11:44,161
Sayang sekali.

172
00:11:44,245 --> 00:11:45,246
Kumohon!

173
00:11:45,413 --> 00:11:49,625
Itu tugas kalian, 'kan?
Pergilah dan bunuh dia!

174
00:11:50,251 --> 00:11:51,877
Meskipun aku ingin,

175
00:11:52,336 --> 00:11:56,465
kami baru selesai memotong tangkapan kami,
dan kami belum mengisi bahan bakar.

176
00:11:56,549 --> 00:11:58,592
Tak perlu terlalu khawatir.

177
00:11:58,801 --> 00:12:01,262
Hanya sedikit yang menyerang manusia.

178
00:12:01,679 --> 00:12:03,764
Juga, naga itu belum tentu akan...

179
00:12:03,848 --> 00:12:06,434
Putriku dan suaminya tinggal di sana!

180
00:12:06,517 --> 00:12:09,186
- Jika terjadi sesuatu pada mereka...
- Tapi...

181
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:11,897
Inilah fungsinya pemburu naga!

182
00:12:11,981 --> 00:12:14,650
- Beraninya kau!
- Ayo.

183
00:12:15,192 --> 00:12:17,903
Mika! Kita belum selesai isi pasokan.

184
00:12:18,237 --> 00:12:19,488
Hanya di kota sebelah.

185
