Dia memanggil kawannya.

214
00:14:11,058 --> 00:14:11,976
Sungguh?

215
00:14:12,601 --> 00:14:13,894
Ya, mungkin.

216
00:14:14,812 --> 00:14:15,813
Firasat saja.

217
00:14:16,522 --> 00:14:19,149
- "Mungkin"?
- Dia punya firasat soal naga.

218
00:14:19,233 --> 00:14:21,151
