di atas kota.

222
00:14:33,372 --> 00:14:34,248
Mustahil.

223
00:14:34,957 --> 00:14:38,252
Kita harus bergegas.
Jika tak bergegas, tamatlah kita!

224
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:40,504
Mika!

225
00:14:46,135 --> 00:14:48,762
